Package Deal S01E11 - It's My Party (REAL)

Sheldon lands a party-planning gig for an important judge who Danny is out to impress; at the same time, Ryan faces losing another therapist, but gaining a romantic interest.

This episode aired on CityTV on Jan 2, 2014. The quality is something like V8 A8 since this was recorded from a non-HD channel via analog methods.

The reason for calling this "REAL" is that 2HD missed this episode, and their episode numbering is thus off by one. 2HD's S01E11 is episode 12 ("Sick Puppy") and their S01E12 is episode 13 ("Kangaroo Court").
